metadata.description:
SWARMが提供する最初のコレクション。

このNFTを持ってるとSWARMのディスコード内でファミリーロールをもらえ、ほぼすべての部屋を見られる権限が得られます。

This is the first project collection offered by SWARM.

If you have this NFT, you will receive a family role within the SWARM discord, and you will be authorized to see almost every room.  
https://discord.gg/NByUqjEpgf

The owner of this NFT may use this NFT as a design for any production, commercial or non-commercial, individual or corporate, as long as the use is in accordance with the terms and conditions established by the creator. Copyright is not waived.

Use for purposes offensive to public order and morals  
Offensive, discriminatory, sexual, or extreme use that damages the image of the material  
Use related to antisocial forces or illegal activities  
Any other use deemed inappropriate by the author
